			<span class="text-xl text-stone-900 font-semibold text-center max-w-2xl px-1 pb-10">
				We harness the power of horses to expand opportunities for Central Indiana's youth.
			</span>
			<div class="pb-10">
				<Button href="/donate" target="_self">
					Donate Now
				</Button>
			</div>
			<span class="text-lg text-center text-stone-700 max-w-3xl px-2 pb-10">
